{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Some of you have heard the story before,"},{"time":1960,"text":"but, in fact, there's somebody\nin the audience"},{"time":4160,"text":"who's never heard this story\nin front of an audience before,"},{"time":7040,"text":"so I'm a little more nervous\nthan I normally am telling this story."},{"time":10800,"text":"I used to be a photographer\nfor many years."},{"time":12920,"text":"In 1978, I was working for \"TIME Magazine\""},{"time":15800,"text":"and I was given a three-day assignment\nto photograph Amerasian children,"},{"time":19960,"text":"children who had been fathered\nby American GIs all over Southeast Asia,"},{"time":23320,"text":"and then abandoned --\n40,000 children all over Asia."},{"time":26680,"text":"I had never heard\nthe word Amerasian before."},{"time":29520,"text":"I spent a few days photographing\nchildren in different countries,"},{"time":33080,"text":"and like a lot of photographers\nand a lot of journalists,"},{"time":36360,"text":"I always hoped that\nwhen my pictures are published,"},{"time":38840,"text":"they might actually\nhave an effect on a situation,"},{"time":41240,"text":"instead of just documenting it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42800,"text":"So, I was so disturbed by what I saw"},{"time":47080,"text":"and I was so unhappy\nwith the article that ran afterwards,"},{"time":51200,"text":"that I decided\nI would take six months off."},{"time":53680,"text":"I was 28 years old."},{"time":55120,"text":"I decided I would find\nsix children in different countries,"},{"time":58880,"text":"and actually go spend\nsome time with the kids,"},{"time":61080,"text":"and try to tell their story\na little bit better"},{"time":63320,"text":"than I thought I had done\nfor Time magazine."},{"time":66320,"text":"In the course of doing the story,"},{"time":67960,"text":"I was looking for children\nwho hadn't been photographed before,"},{"time":73640,"text":"and the Pearl Buck Foundation told me\nthat they worked with a lot of Americans"},{"time":78600,"text":"who were donating money\nto help some of these kids."},{"time":81040,"text":"And a man told me,"},{"time":82320,"text":"who ran the Pearl Buck\nFoundation in Korea,"},{"time":85000,"text":"that there was a young girl,\nwho was 11 years old,"},{"time":87400,"text":"being raised by her grandmother."},{"time":89000,"text":"And the grandmother\nhad never let any Westerners see her."},{"time":91720,"text":"Every time any Westerners\ncame to the village, she hid the girl."},{"time":94800,"text":"Of course, I was immediately intrigued."},{"time":96720,"text":"I saw photographs of her\nand I thought I wanted to go."},{"time":99320,"text":"And the guy just told me,"},{"time":100600,"text":"\"This grandmother -- there's no way\nshe's ever going to let you"},{"time":103600,"text":"meet this girl that's she's raising.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":105440,"text":"I took a translator with me\nand went to this village,"},{"time":107960,"text":"found the grandmother, sat down with her."},{"time":109960,"text":"And to my astonishment, she agreed\nto let me photograph her granddaughter."},{"time":113480,"text":"And I was paying for this myself,\nso I asked the translator"},{"time":116320,"text":"if it would be OK\nif I stayed for the week."},{"time":118360,"text":"I had a sleeping bag."},{"time":120000,"text":"The family had a small shed\non the side of the house,"},{"time":122720,"text":"so I said, \"Could I sleep\nin my sleeping bag in the evenings?\""},{"time":125920,"text":"And I just told the little girl,\nwhose name was Eun-Sook Lee,"},{"time":130880,"text":"that if I ever did anything\nto embarrass her --"},{"time":133120,"text":"she didn't speak a word of English,\nalthough she looked very American --"},{"time":136560,"text":"she could put up her hand and say, \"Stop,\"\nand I would stop taking pictures."},{"time":140160,"text":"Then my translator left.\nI couldn't speak a word of Korean."},{"time":143000,"text":"This is the first night I met Eun-Sook."},{"time":144960,"text":"Her mother was still alive."},{"time":146320,"text":"She was not raising her,\nher grandmother was raising her."},{"time":149040,"text":"And what struck me immediately"},{"time":151360,"text":"was how in love\nthe two of these people were."},{"time":154840,"text":"The grandmother was incredibly fond,\ndeeply in love with this little girl."},{"time":159080,"text":"They slept on the floor at night."},{"time":160720,"text":"The way they heat their homes in Korea\nis to put bricks under the floors,"},{"time":164200,"text":"so the heat radiates\nfrom underneath the floor."},{"time":166440,"text":"Eun-Sook was 11 years old."}]},{"cues":[{"time":167800,"text":"I had photographed,\nas I said, a lot of these kids."},{"time":170240,"text":"Eun-Sook was the fifth child\nthat I found to photograph."},{"time":173240,"text":"And almost universally,\namongst all the kids,"},{"time":175800,"text":"they were really psychologically damaged"},{"time":178520,"text":"by having been made fun of,\nridiculed, picked on and been rejected."},{"time":182360,"text":"And Korea was probably the place\nI found to be the worst for these kids."},{"time":186160,"text":"And what struck me immediately\nin meeting Eun-Sook"},{"time":189360,"text":"was how confident she appeared to be,"},{"time":191200,"text":"how happy she seemed to be\nin her own skin."},{"time":193440,"text":"And remember this picture,"},{"time":194720,"text":"because I'm going to show you\nanother picture later."},{"time":197200,"text":"She looks much like her grandmother,\nalthough she looks so Western."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200400,"text":"I decided to follow her to school."},{"time":202080,"text":"This is the first morning\nI stayed with her."},{"time":204200,"text":"This is on the way to school."},{"time":205640,"text":"This is the morning assembly\noutside her school."},{"time":211840,"text":"And I noticed that\nshe was clowning around."},{"time":215360,"text":"When the teachers would ask questions,"},{"time":217240,"text":"she'd be the first person\nto raise her hand."},{"time":219680,"text":"Again, not at all shy or withdrawn,"},{"time":221640,"text":"or anything like the other children\nthat I'd photographed."},{"time":224400,"text":"The first one to go\nto the blackboard to answer questions."},{"time":227160,"text":"Getting in trouble for whispering\ninto her best friend's ears."},{"time":230120,"text":"And one of the other things\nI said to her through the translator --"},{"time":233320,"text":"again, this thing about saying stop --\nwas to not pay attention to me."},{"time":237920,"text":"So she really just completely\nignored me most of the time."},{"time":240760,"text":"I noticed that at recess,"},{"time":242000,"text":"she was the girl who picked\nthe other girls to be on her team."},{"time":245840,"text":"It was very obvious, from the beginning,\nthat she was a leader."},{"time":248840,"text":"This is on the way home.\nAnd that's North Korea up along the hill."},{"time":252000,"text":"This is up along the DMZ."},{"time":253240,"text":"They would actually\ncover the windows every night,"},{"time":255640,"text":"so that light couldn't be seen,"},{"time":257200,"text":"because the South Korean government\nhas said for years"},{"time":259760,"text":"that the North Koreans\nmay invade at any time."},{"time":261959,"text":"So the closer you were to North Korea,\nthe more terrifying it was."}]},{"cues":[{"time":265280,"text":"Very often at school,\nI'd be taking pictures,"},{"time":267600,"text":"and she would whisper\ninto her girlfriends' ears,"},{"time":269960,"text":"and then look at me and say, \"Stop.\""},{"time":271800,"text":"And I would stand at attention,\nand all the girls would crack up,"},{"time":274880,"text":"and it was sort of a little joke."}]},{"cues":[{"time":276520,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":277920,"text":"The end of the week came\nand my translator came back,"},{"time":280440,"text":"because I'd asked her to come back,"},{"time":282160,"text":"so I could formally thank\nthe grandmother and Eun-Sook."},{"time":284920,"text":"And in the course of the grandmother\ntalking to the translator,"},{"time":288200,"text":"the grandmother started crying."},{"time":289920,"text":"And I said to my translator,\n\"What's going on, why is she crying?\""},{"time":293080,"text":"And she spoke to\nthe grandmother for a moment,"},{"time":295280,"text":"and then she started\ngetting tears in her eyes."},{"time":297520,"text":"And I said, \"What did I do?\nWhy is everyone crying?\""},{"time":300000,"text":"And the translator said,"},{"time":301240,"text":"\"The grandmother says\nthat she thinks she's dying,"},{"time":304080,"text":"and she wants to know if you would take\nEun-Sook to America with you.\""},{"time":308600,"text":"And I said, \"I'm 28 years old\nand I live in hotels,"},{"time":313920,"text":"and I'm not married.\""},{"time":315760,"text":"I mean, I had fallen in love\nwith this girl,"},{"time":318000,"text":"but you know, emotionally\nI was about 12 years old."},{"time":320960,"text":"If you know of photographers,"},{"time":322560,"text":"the joke is it's the finest form\nof delayed adolescence ever invented."},{"time":327000,"text":"\"Sorry, I have to go\non an assignment, I'll be back\" --"},{"time":329640,"text":"and then you never come back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":331080,"text":"So I asked the translator\nwhy she thought she was dying."},{"time":336400,"text":"Can I get her to a hospital?\nCould I pay to get her a doctor?"},{"time":339320,"text":"And she refused any help at all."},{"time":341360,"text":"So when I got outside,\nI gave the translator some money and said,"},{"time":344544,"text":"\"Go back and see if you can do something.\""},{"time":346664,"text":"And I gave the grandmother\nmy business card."},{"time":348760,"text":"And I said, \"If you're serious,\nI will try to find a family for her.\""},{"time":352040,"text":"And I immediately wrote a letter\nto my best friends in Atlanta, Georgia,"},{"time":355480,"text":"who had an 11-year-old son."},{"time":356840,"text":"And my best friend\nhad mistakenly one day said something"},{"time":360320,"text":"about wishing he had another child."},{"time":362840,"text":"So my friends Gene and Gayle\nhad not heard from me in about a year,"},{"time":366920,"text":"and suddenly I was calling,"},{"time":368360,"text":"saying \"I'm in Korea\nand I've met this extraordinary girl.\""},{"time":371640,"text":"And I said, \"The grandmother\nthinks she's sick,"},{"time":374360,"text":"but I think maybe we would have to\nbring the grandmother over also.\""},{"time":377880,"text":"And I said, \"I'll pay for the ... \"\nI mean, I had this whole sort of picture."},{"time":381560,"text":"So anyway, I left."},{"time":382840,"text":"And my friends actually said\nthey were very interested in adopting her."},{"time":388360,"text":"And I said, \"Look, I think\nI'll scare the grandmother to death,"},{"time":391360,"text":"if I tell her that\nyou're willing to adopt her."},{"time":393960,"text":"I want to go back and talk to her.\"\nBut I was off on assignment."},{"time":397000,"text":"I figured I'd come back\nin a couple of weeks"},{"time":399120,"text":"and talk to the grandmother."}]},{"cues":[{"time":400520,"text":"And on Christmas Day, I was in Bangkok\nwith a group of photographers"},{"time":403760,"text":"and got a telegram --\nback in those days, you got telegrams --"},{"time":406720,"text":"from Time magazine\nsaying someone in Korea had died"},{"time":409160,"text":"and left their child in a will to me."},{"time":411440,"text":"Did I know anything about this?"},{"time":413000,"text":"Because I hadn't told them\nwhat I was doing,"},{"time":415120,"text":"because I was so upset\nwith the story they'd run."},{"time":417680,"text":"So, I went back to Korea,\nand I went back to Eun-Sook's village,"},{"time":421080,"text":"and she was gone."},{"time":422320,"text":"And the house that\nI had spent time in was empty."},{"time":425040,"text":"It was incredibly cold."},{"time":426680,"text":"No one in the village\nwould tell me where Eun-Sook was,"},{"time":429320,"text":"because the grandmother\nhad always hidden her from Westerners."},{"time":432280,"text":"And they had no idea\nabout this request that she'd made of me."},{"time":435240,"text":"So I finally found Myung Sung,"},{"time":437080,"text":"her best friend that she used to play with\nafter school every day."},{"time":440240,"text":"And Myung Sung, under some pressure\nfrom me and the translator,"},{"time":443240,"text":"gave us an address\non the outside of Seoul."},{"time":445640,"text":"And I went to that address\nand knocked on the door,"},{"time":450280,"text":"and a man answered the door."},{"time":451680,"text":"It was not a very nice area of Seoul,\nthere were mud streets outside of it."},{"time":456600,"text":"And I knocked on the door\nand Eun-Sook answered the door,"},{"time":459320,"text":"and her eyes were bloodshot,\nand she seemed to be in shock."},{"time":462120,"text":"She didn't recognize me --\nthere was no recognition whatsoever."},{"time":465120,"text":"And this man came to the door\nand kind of barked something in Korean."},{"time":468400,"text":"And I said to the translator,\n\"What did he say?\""},{"time":470680,"text":"And she said, \"He wants\nto know who you are.\""},{"time":472840,"text":"And I said, \"Tell him\nthat I am a photographer.\""},{"time":475120,"text":"I started explaining who I was,\nand he interrupted."},{"time":477560,"text":"And she said, \"He says he knows\nwho you are, what do you want?\""},{"time":480560,"text":"I said, \"Well, tell him that I was asked\nby this little girl's grandmother"},{"time":485040,"text":"to find a family for her.\""},{"time":487000,"text":"And he said, \"I'm her uncle,\nshe's fine, you can leave now.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":492000,"text":"So I was --"},{"time":494520,"text":"The door was being slammed in my face,"},{"time":496400,"text":"it's incredibly cold,\nand I'm trying to think,"},{"time":498600,"text":"\"What would the hero do in a movie,\nif I was writing this as a movie script?\""},{"time":502280,"text":"So I said, \"It's really cold,\nI've come a very long way,"},{"time":504960,"text":"do you mind if I come in\nfor a minute? I'm freezing.\""},{"time":507480,"text":"So the guy reluctantly let us in\nand we sat down on the floor."},{"time":510440,"text":"And as we started talking,\nI saw him yell something,"},{"time":512919,"text":"and Eun-Sook came\nand brought us some food."},{"time":515720,"text":"And I had this whole mental picture\nof -- sort of like Cinderella."},{"time":519080,"text":"I sort of had this picture\nof this incredibly wonderful,"},{"time":522600,"text":"bright, happy little child,"},{"time":524600,"text":"who now appeared to be very withdrawn,\nbeing enslaved by this family."},{"time":529600,"text":"And I was really appalled,\nand I couldn't figure out what to do."},{"time":532680,"text":"And the more I tried talking to him,\nthe less friendly he was getting."},{"time":536000,"text":"So finally I said \"Look,\" --\nthis is all through the translator,"},{"time":539040,"text":"because, you know,\nI don't speak a word of Korean --"},{"time":541520,"text":"and I said, \"Look, I'm really glad\nthat Eun-Sook has a family to live with."},{"time":545840,"text":"I was very worried about her."},{"time":547280,"text":"I made a promise to her grandmother,\nyour mother, that I would find a family,"},{"time":550960,"text":"and I'm so happy that\nyou're going to take care of her."},{"time":553600,"text":"But I bought an airline ticket\nand I'm stuck here for a week."},{"time":556520,"text":"I'm staying in a hotel downtown."},{"time":558120,"text":"Would you like to come\nand have lunch tomorrow?"},{"time":560360,"text":"And you can practice your English.\""},{"time":562080,"text":"Because he told me -- I was trying\nto ask him questions about himself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":565400,"text":"And so I went to the hotel,\nand I found two older Amerasians."},{"time":569520,"text":"A girl whose mother had been a prostitute,"},{"time":574000,"text":"and she was a prostitute,"},{"time":575880,"text":"and a boy who'd been in and out of jail."},{"time":577840,"text":"And I said to them,\n\"Look, there's a little girl"},{"time":580160,"text":"who has a tiny chance\nof getting out of here"},{"time":583320,"text":"and going to America."},{"time":584600,"text":"I don't know if it's\nthe right decision or not,"},{"time":586960,"text":"but I would like you\nto come to lunch tomorrow"},{"time":589160,"text":"and tell the uncle what it's like\nto walk down the street,"},{"time":591920,"text":"what people say to you,\nwhat you do for a living."},{"time":594520,"text":"I want him to understand\nwhat happens if she stays here."},{"time":597560,"text":"And I could be wrong, I don't know,\nbut I wish you would come tomorrow.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":601000,"text":"So, these two came to lunch\nand we got thrown out of the restaurant."},{"time":604840,"text":"They were yelling at him,\nit got to be really ugly."},{"time":608320,"text":"We went outside, and he was just furious."},{"time":610297,"text":"And I knew I had totally blown this thing."},{"time":612360,"text":"Here I was again,\ntrying to figure out what to do."},{"time":614760,"text":"And he started yelling at me,\nand I said to the translator,"},{"time":617600,"text":"\"Tell him to calm down,\nwhat is he saying?\""},{"time":619640,"text":"And she said, \"He's saying, 'Who the hell\nare you to walk into my house,"},{"time":623080,"text":"some rich American\nwith your cameras around your neck,"},{"time":625640,"text":"accusing me of enslaving my niece?"},{"time":628360,"text":"This is my niece, I love her,\nshe's my sister's daughter."},{"time":631686,"text":"Who the hell are you\nto accuse me of something like this?'\""},{"time":636120,"text":"And I said, you know,\n\"Look, you're absolutely right."},{"time":639000,"text":"I don't pretend to understand\nwhat's going on here."},{"time":641440,"text":"All I know is, I've been\nphotographing a lot of these children."},{"time":644440,"text":"I'm in love with your niece,"},{"time":647400,"text":"I think she's an incredibly\nspecial child.\""},{"time":649760,"text":"And I said, \"Look, I will fly my friends\nover here from the United States"},{"time":653240,"text":"if you want to meet them,\nto see if you approve of them."},{"time":655920,"text":"I just think that --\nwhat little I know about the situation,"},{"time":659560,"text":"she has very little chance here\nof having the kind of life"},{"time":662320,"text":"that you probably would like her to have.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":664360,"text":"So, everyone told me afterwards\nthat inviting the prospective parents over"},{"time":667880,"text":"was, again, the stupidest thing\nI could have possibly done,"},{"time":670680,"text":"because who's ever\ngood enough for your relative?"},{"time":673040,"text":"But he invited me to come to a ceremony\nthey were having that day"},{"time":676160,"text":"for her grandmother."},{"time":677560,"text":"And they actually take\nitems of clothing and photographs,"},{"time":680280,"text":"and they burn them as part of the ritual."},{"time":683040,"text":"And you can see how different she looks\njust in three months."},{"time":685960,"text":"This was now, I think, early February."},{"time":688400,"text":"And the pictures before\nwere taken in September."},{"time":692040,"text":"Well, there was\nan American Maryknoll priest"},{"time":694160,"text":"that I had met in the course\nof doing the story,"},{"time":696440,"text":"who had 75 children living in his house."},{"time":698400,"text":"He had three women helping him\ntake care of these kids."},{"time":701040,"text":"And so I suggested to the uncle\nthat we go down and meet Father Keane"},{"time":704320,"text":"to find out how\nthe adoption process worked."},{"time":706440,"text":"Because I wanted him to feel"},{"time":707840,"text":"like this was all being done\nvery much above board."}]},{"cues":[{"time":710280,"text":"So, this is on the way\ndown to the orphanage."},{"time":713000,"text":"This is Father Keane.\nHe's just a wonderful guy."},{"time":718080,"text":"He had kids from\nall over Korea living there,"},{"time":720360,"text":"and he would find families for these kids."},{"time":723440,"text":"This is a social worker\ninterviewing Eun-Sook."},{"time":725920,"text":"Now, I had always thought she was\ncompletely untouched by all of this,"},{"time":729360,"text":"because the grandmother, to me,"},{"time":730880,"text":"appeared to be sort of\nthe village wise woman --"},{"time":734480,"text":"throughout the day, I noticed people\nkept coming to visit her grandmother."},{"time":738000,"text":"And I always had this mental picture"},{"time":739760,"text":"that even though they may have been\none of the poorer families in the village,"},{"time":743480,"text":"they were one of the most respected."},{"time":745240,"text":"And I always felt that the grandmother\nhad kind of demanded, and insisted,"},{"time":748840,"text":"that the villagers treat Eun-Sook\nwith the same respect they treated her."},{"time":754240,"text":"Eun-Sook stayed at Father Keane's,"},{"time":756360,"text":"and her uncle agreed to let her stay there\nuntil the adoption went through."},{"time":759960,"text":"He actually agreed to the adoption."}]},{"cues":[{"time":761840,"text":"And I went off on assignment\nand came back a week later,"},{"time":764520,"text":"and Father Keane said,\n\"I've got to talk to you about Eun-Sook.\""},{"time":767560,"text":"I said, \"Oh God, now what?\""},{"time":768920,"text":"And he takes me into this room,\ncloses the door and says,"},{"time":771640,"text":"\"I have 75 children here in the orphanage,\nand it's total bedlam.\""},{"time":774800,"text":"There's clothes, there's kids."},{"time":776280,"text":"Three adults and 75 kids --\nyou can imagine."},{"time":778640,"text":"And he said, \"The second day\nshe was here she made up a list"},{"time":781520,"text":"of all of the names\nof the older kids and the younger kids."},{"time":784520,"text":"And she assigned one of the older kids\nto each of the younger kids."},{"time":788080,"text":"And then she set up a work detail list\nof who cleaned the orphanage on what day.\""},{"time":792680,"text":"And he said, \"She's telling me\nthat I'm messy"},{"time":794840,"text":"and I have to clean up my room.\""},{"time":796440,"text":"And he said, \"I don't know who raised her,\nbut she's running the orphanage,"},{"time":800040,"text":"and she's been here three days.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":801640,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":803120,"text":"This was movie day that she organized\nwhere all the kids went to the movies."},{"time":808200,"text":"A lot of the kids who had been adopted\nwrote back to the other kids,"},{"time":811440,"text":"telling them what their life\nwas like with their new families."},{"time":814400,"text":"So it was a really big deal\nwhen the letters showed up."},{"time":817040,"text":"This is a woman who is\nnow working at the orphanage,"},{"time":819520,"text":"whose son had been adopted."},{"time":823960,"text":"Gene and Gayle started studying Korean"},{"time":826000,"text":"the moment they had gotten\nmy first letter."},{"time":828040,"text":"They really wanted to be able\nto welcome Eun-Sook into their family."},{"time":832560,"text":"And one of the things Father Keane told me"},{"time":834640,"text":"when I came back\nfrom one of these trips --"},{"time":836680,"text":"Eun-Sook had chosen the name Natasha,"},{"time":838600,"text":"which I understood was from her watching\na \"Rocky and Bullwinkle\" cartoon"},{"time":842880,"text":"on the American Air Force station."},{"time":844840,"text":"This may be one\nof those myth-buster things"},{"time":846920,"text":"that we'll have to\nclear up here, in a minute."}]},{"cues":[{"time":849120,"text":"So, my friend Gene\nflew over with his son, Tim."},{"time":851440,"text":"Gayle couldn't come."},{"time":853000,"text":"And they spent a lot of time\nhuddled over a dictionary."},{"time":855640,"text":"And this was Gene showing the uncle"},{"time":857360,"text":"where Atlanta was on the map,\nwhere he lived."},{"time":860800,"text":"This is the uncle\nsigning the adoption papers."},{"time":863840,"text":"Now, we went out to dinner\nthat night to celebrate."},{"time":866280,"text":"The uncle went back to his family"},{"time":867920,"text":"and Natasha and Tim and Gene and I\nwent out to dinner."},{"time":871400,"text":"And Gene was showing Natasha\nhow to use a knife and fork,"},{"time":875280,"text":"and then Natasha\nwas returning the utensil lessons."},{"time":879960,"text":"We went back to our hotel room,"},{"time":881880,"text":"and Gene was showing Natasha\nalso where Atlanta was."},{"time":884360,"text":"This is the third night we were in Korea."},{"time":886360,"text":"The first night we'd gotten a room\nfor the kids right next to us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":889440,"text":"I'd been staying in this room\nfor about three months --"},{"time":892080,"text":"it was a little 15-story Korean hotel."},{"time":895600,"text":"The second night,\nwe didn't keep the kids' room,"},{"time":898000,"text":"because we slept on the floor\nwith all the kids at the orphanage."},{"time":901120,"text":"And the third night, we came back --"},{"time":902880,"text":"we'd just gone out to dinner,\nwhere you saw the pictures --"},{"time":905680,"text":"and we got to the front desk,\nand the guy said,"},{"time":907920,"text":"\"There's no other free rooms\non your floor tonight,"},{"time":910360,"text":"you can put the kids\nfive floors below you.\""},{"time":912480,"text":"And Gene and I\nlooked at each other and said,"},{"time":914640,"text":"\"We don't want two 11-year-olds\nfive floors away.\""},{"time":917040,"text":"So his son said, \"I have a sleeping bag,\nI'll sleep on the floor.\""},{"time":920200,"text":"And I said, \"I have one too.\"\nSo Tim and I slept on the floor,"},{"time":923160,"text":"Natasha got one bed,\nGene got the other -- kids pass out,"},{"time":925960,"text":"it's been very exciting for three days."}]},{"cues":[{"time":927880,"text":"We're lying in bed, and Gene and I\nare talking about how cool we are."},{"time":931400,"text":"We said, \"That was so great,\nwe saved this little girl's life.\""},{"time":934400,"text":"We were just like,\nyou know, just full of ourselves."},{"time":937880,"text":"And we fall asleep --"},{"time":939240,"text":"and I've been in this room\nfor a couple of months now."},{"time":941840,"text":"And they always overheat\nthe hotels in Korea terribly,"},{"time":945720,"text":"so during the day\nI always left the window open."},{"time":948040,"text":"And then about midnight,\nthey turn the heat off in the hotel."},{"time":950960,"text":"So at 1am, the whole room would be\nlike 20 below zero, and I'd get up."},{"time":954280,"text":"I'd been doing this\nevery night I'd been there."},{"time":956520,"text":"So, sure enough,\nit's one o'clock, room's freezing,"},{"time":959040,"text":"I go to close the window\nand I hear people shouting outside,"},{"time":962760,"text":"and I thought, \"Oh, the bars\nmust have just gotten out.\""},{"time":965404,"text":"I don't speak Korean,\nbut I'm hearing these voices,"},{"time":967840,"text":"and I'm not hearing anger,\nI'm hearing terror."},{"time":971080,"text":"So I open the window and I look out,"},{"time":973200,"text":"and there's flames\ncoming up the side of our hotel,"},{"time":975960,"text":"and the hotel's on fire."},{"time":977680,"text":"So I run over to Gene and I wake him up,"},{"time":979640,"text":"and I say, \"Don't freak out,\nI think the hotel's on fire.\""},{"time":982440,"text":"And now there's smoke and flames\ncoming by our windows --"},{"time":985160,"text":"we're on the 11th floor."},{"time":986440,"text":"So the two of us were just like,\n\"Oh my God, oh my God.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":989120,"text":"So we're trying to get Natasha up,\nand we can't talk to her."},{"time":992520,"text":"You know what kids are like\nwhen they've been asleep for like an hour,"},{"time":995840,"text":"it's like they took five Valiums --\nthey're all over the place."},{"time":998840,"text":"And we can't talk to her."},{"time":1000080,"text":"His son had the L.L.Bean bootlaces,\nand we're trying to do up his laces."},{"time":1003520,"text":"So we try to get to the door,\nwe run to the door, we open the door,"},{"time":1006720,"text":"and it's like walking\ninto a blast furnace."},{"time":1008800,"text":"There's people screaming,\nthe sound of glass breaking, weird thumps."},{"time":1012200,"text":"And the whole room filled\nwith smoke in about two seconds."},{"time":1015040,"text":"And Gene turns around and says,\n\"We're not going to make it.\""},{"time":1017960,"text":"And he closes the door, and the whole room\nis now filled with smoke."},{"time":1021200,"text":"We're all choking, and there's smoke"},{"time":1022960,"text":"pouring through the vents,\nunder the doors."},{"time":1025000,"text":"There's people screaming."},{"time":1026280,"text":"I just remember this unbelievable --\njust utter chaos."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1028920,"text":"I remember sitting near the bed,\nand I had two overwhelming feelings."},{"time":1032440,"text":"One was absolute terror.\n\"Oh, please God, I just want to wake up."},{"time":1035760,"text":"This has got to be a nightmare,\nthis can't be happening."},{"time":1038440,"text":"Please, I just want to wake up.\""},{"time":1040040,"text":"And the other is unbelievable guilt."},{"time":1041800,"text":"Here I've been playing God\nwith my friends' lives,"},{"time":1044200,"text":"my friends' son, with Natasha's life,"},{"time":1046040,"text":"and this what you get when you try\nplaying God, is you hurt people."},{"time":1049360,"text":"I remember just being\nso frightened and terrified."},{"time":1051760,"text":"And Gene, who's lying on the floor, says,"},{"time":1053760,"text":"\"We've got to soak towels.\"\nI said, \"What?\""},{"time":1055840,"text":"\"We've got to soak towels.\nWe're going to die from the smoke.\""},{"time":1058800,"text":"So got towels and put them\nover our faces and the kids' faces."},{"time":1061729,"text":"Then he said, \"Do you have gaffer's tape?\""},{"time":1063800,"text":"\"What?\" \"Do you have gaffer's tape?\""},{"time":1065560,"text":"I said, \"Somewhere in my Halliburton.\""},{"time":1067440,"text":"He says, \"We've got to stop the smoke.\nThat's all we can do.\""},{"time":1070322,"text":"I mean, Gene -- thank God for Gene."},{"time":1072800,"text":"So we put the room service menus\nover the vents in the wall,"},{"time":1077680,"text":"we put blankets at the bottom of the door,"},{"time":1079760,"text":"we put the kids on the windowsill\nto try to get some air."},{"time":1082480,"text":"And there was a new building, going up,"},{"time":1084400,"text":"that was being built\nright across the street from our hotel."},{"time":1087280,"text":"And there, in the building,\nwere photographers,"},{"time":1089495,"text":"waiting for people to jump."},{"time":1091320,"text":"Eleven people ended up dying in the fire."},{"time":1093440,"text":"Five people jumped and died,\nother people were killed by the smoke."},{"time":1097520,"text":"And there's this loud thumping on the door\nafter about 45 minutes in all this,"},{"time":1102520,"text":"and people were shouting in Korean."},{"time":1104240,"text":"And I remember --"},{"time":1109000,"text":"Natasha didn't want us opening the door --"},{"time":1111640,"text":"sorry, I was trying not to open the door,"},{"time":1113640,"text":"because we'd spent so much time\nbarricading the room."},{"time":1116160,"text":"I didn't know who it was,\nI didn't know what they wanted,"},{"time":1118880,"text":"and Natasha could tell\nthey were firemen trying to get us out."},{"time":1121840,"text":"I remember a sort of a tussle at the door,\ntrying to get the door open."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1125200,"text":"In any case, 12 hours later --\nI mean, they put us in the lobby."},{"time":1129640,"text":"Gene ended up using his coat,\nand his fist in the coat,"},{"time":1133280,"text":"to break open a liquor cabinet."},{"time":1134840,"text":"People were lying on the floor."},{"time":1136400,"text":"It was one of just\nthe most horrifying nights."},{"time":1138600,"text":"And then 12 hours later,\nwe rented a car, as we had planned to,"},{"time":1142360,"text":"and drove back to Natasha's village."},{"time":1144360,"text":"And we kept saying, \"Do you realize\nwe were dying in a hotel fire,"},{"time":1147520,"text":"like eight hours ago?\""},{"time":1148760,"text":"It's so weird how life just goes on."},{"time":1150520,"text":"Natasha wanted to introduce her brother\nand father to all the villagers,"},{"time":1153960,"text":"and the day we showed up turned out\nto be a 60-year-old man's birthday."},{"time":1157320,"text":"This guy's 60 years old."},{"time":1158560,"text":"So it turned into a dual celebration,"},{"time":1160360,"text":"because Natasha was\nthe first person from this village"},{"time":1162920,"text":"ever to go to the United States."},{"time":1164520,"text":"So, these are the greenhouse tents."},{"time":1166240,"text":"This is the elders\nteaching Gene their dances."},{"time":1168440,"text":"We drank a lot of rice wine."},{"time":1169840,"text":"We were both so drunk,\nI couldn't believe it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1175760,"text":"This is the last picture\nbefore Gene and Tim headed back."},{"time":1178760,"text":"The adoption people told us"},{"time":1180440,"text":"it was going to take a year\nfor the adoption to go through."},{"time":1184080,"text":"Like, what could you do for a year?"},{"time":1185960,"text":"So I found out the name of every official\non both the Korean and American side,"},{"time":1189720,"text":"and I photographed them,"},{"time":1191000,"text":"and told them how famous they were\ngoing to be when this book was done."},{"time":1194360,"text":"And four months later,\nthe adoption papers came through."},{"time":1198240,"text":"This is saying goodbye\nto everybody at the orphanage."},{"time":1201440,"text":"This is Father Keane with Natasha\nat the bus stop."},{"time":1204800,"text":"Her great aunt at the airport."},{"time":1206560,"text":"I had a wonderful deal with Cathay Pacific\nairlines for many years,"},{"time":1210000,"text":"where they gave me free passes\non all their airlines"},{"time":1213040,"text":"in return for photography."},{"time":1214360,"text":"It was like the ultimate perk."},{"time":1216160,"text":"And the pilot, I actually knew --"},{"time":1218080,"text":"because they used to let me sit\nin the jump seat,"},{"time":1220440,"text":"to tell you how long ago this was."},{"time":1222120,"text":"This is a TriStar, and so they let Natasha\nactually sit in the jump seat."},{"time":1225600,"text":"And the pilot, Jeff Cowley,\nactually went back"},{"time":1227800,"text":"and adopted one of the other kids\nat the orphanage after meeting Natasha."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1231920,"text":"This is 28 hours later in Atlanta."},{"time":1234000,"text":"It's a very long flight."},{"time":1235440,"text":"Just to make things even crazier,\nGayle, Natasha's new mom,"},{"time":1238800,"text":"was three days away\nfrom giving birth to her own daughter."},{"time":1242760,"text":"You know, if you were\nwriting this, you'd say,"},{"time":1244960,"text":"\"No, we've got to write\nthe script differently.\""},{"time":1247240,"text":"This is the first night showing Natasha\nher new cousins and uncles and aunts."},{"time":1250960,"text":"Gene and Gayle know everyone in Atlanta --\nthey're the most social couple imaginable."},{"time":1255040,"text":"So, at this point, Natasha\ndoesn't speak a word of English,"},{"time":1257981,"text":"other than what little\nFather Keane taught her."},{"time":1261000,"text":"This is Kylie, her sister,\nwho's now a doctor, on the right."},{"time":1267440,"text":"This is a deal I had with Natasha,\nwhich is that when we got to Atlanta"},{"time":1270880,"text":"she could cut off my beard."},{"time":1273560,"text":"She never liked it very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1276440,"text":"She learned English in three months."},{"time":1278240,"text":"She entered seventh grade\nat her own age level."},{"time":1283200,"text":"Pledge of Allegiance for the first time."},{"time":1285160,"text":"This is her cooking teacher."},{"time":1286560,"text":"Natasha told me a lot of the kids\nthought she was stuck up,"},{"time":1289400,"text":"because they would talk to her\nand she wouldn't answer,"},{"time":1292040,"text":"and they didn't realize\nshe didn't speak English very well."},{"time":1294840,"text":"But what I noticed, again as an observer,"},{"time":1296840,"text":"was she was choosing\nwho was going to be on her team,"},{"time":1301320,"text":"and seemed to be very popular\nvery, very quickly."},{"time":1305040,"text":"Now, remember the picture,"},{"time":1306360,"text":"how much she looked like\nher grandmother, at the beginning?"},{"time":1309160,"text":"People were always telling Natasha\nhow much she looks like her mother, Gayle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1312840,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1314880,"text":"This is a tense moment\nin the first football game, I think."},{"time":1320880,"text":"And Kylie -- I mean, it was\nalmost like Kylie was her own child."},{"time":1330040,"text":"She's being baptized."},{"time":1332840,"text":"Now, a lot of parents, when they adopt,"},{"time":1334760,"text":"actually want to erase\ntheir children's history."},{"time":1337040,"text":"And Gayle and Gene\ndid the complete opposite."},{"time":1339200,"text":"They were studying Korean;\nthey bought Korean clothes."},{"time":1341800,"text":"Gene even did a little\ntile work in the kitchen,"},{"time":1344080,"text":"which was that, \"Once upon a time,\nthere was a beautiful girl"},{"time":1347000,"text":"that came from the hills of Korea\nto live happily ever after in Atlanta.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1350453,"text":"She hates this picture --\nit was her first job."},{"time":1352693,"text":"She bought a bright red Karmann Ghia"},{"time":1355120,"text":"with the money she made\nworking at Burger King."},{"time":1357520,"text":"The captain of the cheerleaders."},{"time":1359840,"text":"Beauty pageant."},{"time":1362640,"text":"Used to do their\nChristmas card every year."},{"time":1364800,"text":"Gene's been restoring this car\nfor a million years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1371000,"text":"Kodak hired Natasha to be a translator\nfor them at the Olympics in Korea."},{"time":1375160,"text":"Her future husband, Jeff,\nwas working for Canon cameras,"},{"time":1380080,"text":"and met Natasha at the Olympic Village."},{"time":1383600,"text":"This is her first trip back to Korea.\nSo there's her uncle."},{"time":1387520,"text":"This is her half sister."},{"time":1390560,"text":"She went back to the village."},{"time":1392000,"text":"That's her best friend's mother."},{"time":1395840,"text":"And I always thought that was\na very Annie Hall kind of outfit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1399160,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1401160,"text":"It's just, you know, it was\njust so interesting, just to watch --"},{"time":1404240,"text":"this is her mother\nin the background there."},{"time":1411207,"text":"This is Natasha's wedding day."},{"time":1417800,"text":"Gene is looking a little older."},{"time":1430760,"text":"This is Sydney, who's going to be\nthree years old in a couple of days."},{"time":1436120,"text":"And there's Evan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1438720,"text":"And Natasha, would you\njust come up, for a second,"},{"time":1441280,"text":"just maybe to say hello to everybody?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1443120,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1453520,"text":"Natasha's actually\nnever heard me tell the story."},{"time":1455880,"text":"You know, we've looked\nat the pictures together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1458160,"text":"Natasha: I've seen pictures\nmillions of times,"},{"time":1460360,"text":"but today was the first time I'm actually\nseeing him give the whole presentation."},{"time":1465040,"text":"I started crying."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1466920,"text":"Rick Smolan: There's about 40 things\nshe's going to tell me,"},{"time":1469800,"text":"\"That wasn't what happened.\"\nNatasha: I'll tell you that later."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1473160,"text":"RS: Anyway, thank you, Mike and Richard,\nso much for letting us tell the story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1477080,"text":"Thank you, all of you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1478360,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}